{"tid":1831410,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[831]逾百抗爭者太子站黑夜路軌逃亡的真相!不存在的地底人!","createTime":"2020-01-20T11:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:44.000Z","uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"095fc6d06159983849eea4f7de9a49e160d4bac4","tid":1831410,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190901/UEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190901%2FUEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV90YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=0d8840a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190901%2FUEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI%2F&h=7bb7ac9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190901/UEY5W5NMP3IGEF35VQ4TS54XDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n事由<br />\n當日有人自稱831苦主報料比apple「我地（哋）百幾人行緊地鐵路軌走，有好多傷者，而家個個站都有防暴等緊我地（哋），大圍捕」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家知唔知黑警有n個警區<br />\n其中一個狗力好足, 狗隊好自豪的叫鐵路狗區<br />\n你成百人走當班狗唔識call機夾你,黑警惡毒=/=智障<br />\n事後有人書面問apple 記者班人最後點而apple完全無回應, 因為報料人過去/現在乃至未來皆查無此人<br />\n<br />\n<ins>真相好可能係831傷者部分早已不在人世,政府要製作一個故事合理化呢班人的消失</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>831連日封站就係要把逆向用科學方法清洗現場, 永遠消滅死者曾在現場出現的痕跡</strong>"},{"pid":"4dd9d460351d4ba5554d61b485392318adb0e8b2","tid":1831410,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}